This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-kiss layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============

  Internal dependency on meta-kiss.

  URI: https://git.openembedded.org/openembedded-core
  branch: scarthgap

  URI: git://git.yoctoproject.org/meta-arm
  branch: scarthgap

Patches
=======

Please submit any patches against the meta-kiss layer as patches to
feedback@bootlin.com or as github pull requests at
https://github.com/bootlin/yocto-kiss

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-kiss-nxp layer to your build
 II. Misc


I. Adding the meta-kiss-nxp layer to your build
======================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-kiss-nxp'

II. Misc
========

This layer extend the simple meta-kiss layer with more complex
architectures that need specific firmwares with more nested boot flow.
It is not useful as is, but rather as a reference on how a layer can
be written without unnecessary complications.
